<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT29">
<l>ukappuruvan tāṉē oḷiyuruvan tāṉē</l>
<l>makappuruvan tāṉē matikkil mikappuruva</l>
<l>moṉṟukkoṉ ṟōcaṉaiyāṉ vīḻa vorukaṇaiyā</l>
<l>laṉṟikkoṇ ṭeytā ṉavaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one considers [it], [Rāma]—who, getting very angry, discharged one arrow</l>
<l>so that [Kumbhakarṇa], with a yojanā’s [distance] between [his] one eyebrow</l>
<l>and the [other] fell—</l>
<l>is the one with a pleasing, lustrous, and great form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
